V0511_01_00_00_0.text:
Hi! I'm Rin!
I'm ready to Duel if you are!

V0511_01_00_02_0.text: My dream is to Duel Jack, so I'm no slouch!

V0511_01_00_03_0.text: The Commons take a back seat to no one!

V0511_01_00_04_0.text: My Windwitches will whip up a storm that'll blow you away!

V0511_01_00_05_0.text:
Bring it on, Yugo!
I love knocking you down!

V0511_01_00_06_0.text: I'll test you to see how much stronger you've become!

V0511_01_00_06_1.text: I hope you surprise me, Yugo!

V0511_01_00_07_0.text:
I get to Duel against Jack...
I'm not dreaming, am I?

V0511_01_00_08_0.text:
It's so weird.
I feel like I'm Dueling against myself!

V0511_01_00_09_0.text:
I'm not going to lose against you this time!
You hear me!?

V0511_03_00_00_0.text:
You don't have much LP left...
It's time to end this!

V0511_03_00_01_0.text: I like how you're not willing to give up!

V0511_03_00_04_0.text:
The Duel isn't over yet!
Not by a long shot!

V0511_03_00_05_0.text: I'm just giving you a handicap!

V0511_05_00_00_0.text:
It's not over unless I surrender!
I'll win with this draw!

V0511_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0511_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0511_16_00_00_0.text: There's nothing you can do to stop me!

V0511_21_00_00_0.text:
I have to stay alert...
Can't lose focus now!

V0511_21_00_01_0.text: You're allowed to surrender, you know.

V0511_21_00_04_0.text:
Just focus on winning...
Don't think about anything else!

V0511_21_00_05_0.text: I'm not known to give up either!

V0511_28_00_00_0.text:
Yeah!
My Windwitches were playing great!

V0511_28_00_01_0.text:
I enjoyed this Duel!
Thanks for making it fun!

V0511_28_00_02_0.text: I Duel for my dream - no matter what world I'm in!

V0511_28_00_03_0.text: Since my closest friend will never give up, I can't either.

V0511_28_00_04_0.text: My Windwitches were no breeze, were they.

V0511_28_00_05_0.text: When I see even the slightest opening, I go for it!

V0511_28_00_06_0.text:
Hahaha!
I win this tussle, Yugo!

V0511_28_00_07_0.text:
Sheesh, Yugo.
I know you can play better than this!

V0511_28_00_08_0.text: Only you can snatch defeat from the jaws of victory.

V0511_28_00_08_1.text: Stop getting distracted and just focus on winning!

V0511_28_00_09_0.text:
I think we're more different than the same.
Like sisters!

V0511_29_00_00_0.text:
Sigh...
I lost...
That's too bad.

V0511_29_00_01_0.text:
I won't lose next time!
You can count on it!

V0511_29_00_02_0.text:
I thought I was playing well...
Where did I go wrong?

V0511_29_00_03_0.text: Yugo's gonna give me an earful about how bad I played.

V0511_29_00_04_0.text:
I didn't know you could Duel like that!
I learned a lot!

V0511_29_00_05_0.text: No matter how tough it gets, you never surrender.

V0511_29_00_06_0.text:
Hey!
You're getting good at this!

V0511_33_00_00_0.text: If there's a chance to win, grab it while you can!

V0511_33_00_02_0.text: Can you keep up with my speed?

V0511_30_00_00_0.text: You get so overconfident that you make silly mistakes!

V0511_30_00_01_0.text: That's a bad habit of yours!

V0511_30_00_02_0.text: Can you make a move sometime this century?

V0511_34_00_00_0.text: No matter how long you think, it won't change anything.

V0511_34_00_01_0.text: We both know I'm going to win, so surrender.

V0511_34_00_02_0.text: The fact you won't surrender is what makes you tough.

V0511_34_00_04_0.text: Don’t you know how worried I was I’d never see you again?

V0511_34_00_05_0.text: Scared out of my mind... Not knowing if...

V0511_34_00_07_0.text: I'll let you decide where we battle.

V0511_34_00_10_0.text:
You think too much.
Just Duel.

V0511_34_00_11_0.text: Face it - you're through. I'll accept your surrender now.

V0511_35_00_00_0.text:
I'm Rin.
I use Synchros - just like Yugo!

V0511_35_00_01_0.text: I'll Duel my own Duel to make my dreams come true!

V0511_36_00_02_0.text:
Sorry about this...
But I know you can win!

V0511_36_00_05_0.text: I'm counting on the fact that you never give up, Yugo!

V0511_08_00_00_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Windwitch Chimes!

V0511_08_00_01_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Icy Breeze Refrain!

V0511_08_00_02_0.text:
I activate my Equip Spell!
Kahyoreigetsu!

V0511_08_00_03_0.text: Kahyoreigetsu's effect activates from my Graveyard!

V0511_08_00_04_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Quill Pen of Gulldos!

V0511_08_00_05_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Summon Storm!

V0511_08_00_06_0.text: I banish Summon Storm from my Graveyard to use its effect!

V0511_08_00_07_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Dwimmered Path!

V0511_08_00_08_0.text:
I activate my Equip Spell!
Wonder Wand!

V0511_08_00_10_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Spellbook of Knowledge!

V0511_08_00_11_1.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Super Rush Headlong!

V0511_08_00_12_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Magical Blast!

V0511_08_00_13_0.text: Magical Blast's effect activates from my Graveyard!

V0511_08_00_14_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Spiritual Wind Art - Miyabi!

V0511_08_00_15_0.text: I activate the Trap, Ring of Destruction!

V0511_08_00_16_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Loop of Destruction!

V0511_08_00_18_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Destruction Ring!

V0511_09_00_00_0.text: Unleash your frosty powers, Winter Bell!

V0511_09_00_01_0.text: Winter Bell can activate its effect during the Battle Phase!

V0511_09_00_02_0.text: Diamond Bell's effect activates when it's Synchro Summoned!

V0511_09_00_03_0.text: Since you took damage, Diamond Bell activates its effect!

V0511_09_00_05_0.text: Crystal Bell's effect activates when it's destroyed!

V0511_09_00_06_0.text: I send Blizzard Bell to the Graveyard to use its effect!

V0511_09_00_07_0.text: Glass Bell's effect activates when it's Summoned!

V0511_09_00_08_0.text: Windwitch - Snow Bell's effect activates from my hand!

V0511_09_00_09_0.text: Windwitch - Ice Bell's effect activates from my hand!

V0511_09_00_10_0.text: I can activate Ice Bell's effect when it's Summoned!

V0511_09_00_11_0.text: Windwitch - Freeze Bell's effect activates from my hand!

V0511_09_00_13_0.text: Lucky Pied Piper activates when it destroys a monster!

V0511_09_00_14_0.text: Fusion Parasite activates when it's Special Summoned!

V0511_09_00_15_0.text: Pilica's effect activates when it's Summoned!

V0511_09_00_16_0.text: I discard Ghost Mourner & Moonlit Chill to use its effect!

V0511_09_00_17_0.text: I Tribute Speedroid Taketomborg to activate its effect!

V0511_09_00_20_0.text: Clear Wing Synchro Dragon activates its effect!

V0511_09_00_21_0.text: Crystal Wing Synchro Dragon activates its effect!

V0511_37_00_00_0.text: Be hit with the power of a wicked wintertime blizzard!

V0511_37_00_01_0.text: The ice crystals glisten across the snowfield!

V0511_37_00_02_0.text: I'll form a monster that’ll send shivers down your spine!

V0511_13_00_02_0.text: The chime that echoes across the land!

V0511_13_00_03_0.text: The Tuner Monster, Windwitch - Blizzard Bell!

V0511_13_00_04_0.text: The Tuner Monster, Windwitch - Glass Bell!

V0511_13_00_05_0.text: The Tuner Monster, Windwitch - Snow Bell!

V0511_13_00_11_0.text: The Tuner Monster, Ghost Mourner & Moonlit Chill!

V0511_13_00_14_0.text: The Tuner Monster, Speedroid Red-Eyed Dice!

V0511_37_00_03_0.text: Beat your wings to whip up a whirlwind of destruction!

V0511_13_00_15_0.text: I know you'd rather fight by my side than with Yugo.

V0511_37_00_04_0.text: Pave the way for the monster forged by raw power!

V0511_13_00_16_0.text: A monster this awesome is wasted on Yugo!

V0511_13_00_16_1.text: Take flight, Level 8 Crystal Wing Synchro Dragon!

V0511_44_00_02_0.text: Only one will rule the Duel...

V0511_44_00_03_0.text: In the ultimate fusion of monsters and mayhem!

V0511_26_00_02_0.text: I can take more than that!

V0511_27_00_02_0.text: If I don't do something soon...
